{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"25":"Chapters on Hajj Rituals"},"section_detail":{"25":{"hadithnumber_first":2882,"hadithnumber_last":3119,"arabicnumber_first":2882,"arabicnumber_last":3119}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":2939,"arabicnumber":2939,"text":"Rapporté par ‘Abdullah bin ‘Abbas : Les Prophètes entraient dans le Haram pieds nus. Ils faisaient le tour de la Maison et accomplissaient tous les rites pieds nus et en marchant","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":25,"hadith":58}}]}